//000000000000a:10:{i:0;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"288985";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:665:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;如图所示为探究加速度与力、质量的关系的实验装置．本实验在消除小车与木板间摩擦对运动的影响的过程中：小车靠近打点计时器的一端应连着纸带且接通电源，小车靠近定滑轮的一端&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;_______&lt;/span&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:45:"河南省周口二中高考物理模拟试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"2";}i:1;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"289001";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:343:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;在“探究加速度与力和质量的关系”的实验中我们采用的中学物理常用的实验方法是&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;______________&lt;/span&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:45:"河南省周口二中高考物理模拟试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"2";}i:2;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"286830";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:441:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;选用天平、秒表和石块等器材，利用自由落体运动规律，可估测井口到水面的深度．若当地的重力加速度为&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;g&lt;/span&gt;，则：①需要测量的物理量是&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;______&lt;/span&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:45:"河南省周口二中高考物理模拟试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}i:3;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"288986";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:1099:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;用&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;DIS&lt;/span&gt;实验研究在作用力一定的情况下，加速度与质量的关系时，我们用了如图所示的装置．&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;）图中&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;P&lt;/span&gt;是挂在绳子下面的砝码，&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;是&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;_______&lt;/span&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:45:"河南省周口二中高考物理模拟试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}i:4;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"288987";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:595:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;如下图所示，为“探究物体质量一定时，加速度与物体受力的关系”的实验装置示意图．①把长木板不带滑轮的一端垫高，其目的是&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;_________&lt;/span&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:45:"河南省周口二中高考物理模拟试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}i:5;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"288988";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:676:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;）在“探究加速度与力、质量的关系”的实验中，该同学要探究小车的加速度&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;和质量&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;M&lt;/span&gt;的关系，应该保持&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;_______________&lt;/span&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:45:"河南省周口二中高考物理模拟试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}i:6;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"288990";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:651:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;在用打点计时器测定匀变速直线运动的加速度的实验中，如图是一次实验所记录的六个计数点（相邻两计数点之间有四个打出的计时点未标出）的数据，则小车的加速度的大小为&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;_____&lt;/span&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:45:"河南省周口二中高考物理模拟试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}i:7;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"288991";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:3897:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;现要验证“当合外力一定时，物体运动的加速度与其质量成反比”这一物理规律．给定的器材如下：一倾角可以调节的长斜面（如图）、小车、计时器一个、米尺、天平、砝码、钩码若干．实验步骤如下（不考虑摩擦力的影响），在空格中填入适当的公式或文字．&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;）用天平测出小车的质量&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;m&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;）让小车自斜面上方一固定点&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;从静止开始下滑到斜面底端&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;，记下所用的时间&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;t&lt;/span&gt;．&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;）用米尺测量&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;与&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;之间的距离&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;．则小车的加速度&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;a=&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;__________&lt;/span&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:45:"河南省周口二中高考物理模拟试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}i:8;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"288992";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:3666:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;下面是几个实验中的一些要求或做法：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;①在探究物体加速度&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;和力&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;F&lt;/span&gt;的关系的实验中，用如图&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;所示的装置．为了使细绳对小车的拉力可以 认为近似等于砝码（包括砝码盘）所受的重力，除了要将木板一端适当垫高以平衡摩擦力外，还必须保 证&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;m&lt;/span&gt;《&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;M&lt;/span&gt;．&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;②在用单摆测定重力加速度&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;g&lt;/span&gt;的实验中，可以根据测量的数据，在&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black; letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;-L&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;为单摆周期，&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;L&lt;/span&gt;为摆长）坐标系中描点，用直尺画一条直线，使尽量多的点落在这条直线上．&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;③在验证动量守恒定律的实验中，让入射球从斜槽上某一点滚下与被碰球发生碰撞，落地时通过复写纸在自纸上留下点迹，重复上述实验多次，用尽可能小的圆将这些点迹包围，用圆心位置代表球的落点．&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white; mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;）以上实验&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;____&lt;/span&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:45:"河南省周口二中高考物理模拟试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}i:9;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"288993";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:2679:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;letter-spacing: .6pt;background:white'&gt;为了测定木块与木板（一端带有光滑滑轮）之间的动摩擦因数，利用手头现有的器材：木块、木板、弹簧秤、刻度尺、细绳、砂桶、细砂，甲、乙两位同学各设计了一个实验方案；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体;color:black'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white'&gt;甲的方案是：如图（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing: .6pt;background:white'&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black; letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white'&gt;）所示，将木板固定在水平桌面上，让砂桶带动木块匀速运行（用肉眼观察）．&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体;color:black'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white'&gt;乙的方案是：如图（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;color:black;letter-spacing: .6pt;background:white'&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black; letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white'&gt;）所示，用弹簧秤水平拉住木块，拉动木板从木块下面抽出的过程中，保持木块不动．&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体;color:black'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;letter-spacing:.6pt; background:white'&gt;你认为谁的实验方案测量误差较小&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size: 11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;color:black; letter-spacing:.6pt;background:white'&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;______&lt;/span&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:45:"河南省周口二中高考物理模拟试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}}
